load ../harness-evidence-fork.maude

--- Coverage: a Managed turn records a hermetic context.bundle row.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-EVIDENCE-FORK :
  managedTurn record
  =>* managedTurn bundleRow .

--- Coverage: a Delegated turn records a provider-assembled attestation row.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-EVIDENCE-FORK :
  delegatedTurn record
  =>* delegatedTurn attestationRow .

--- Bite: a Delegated turn never fabricates a context.bundle. The RESIDUAL soup var
--- makes a `bundleRow` in ANY reachable state a solution, so No solution proves the
--- delegated path emits no hermetic provenance row.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-EVIDENCE-FORK :
  delegatedTurn record
  =>* bundleRow RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite: a Managed turn never emits a provider-assembled attestation.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-HARNESS-EVIDENCE-FORK :
  managedTurn record
  =>* attestationRow RESIDUAL:Cfg .
